    <title>Make Hammer 3 hits combo in Unity</title>
    <link href="/codeArt-TechBlog/2024/06/28/Make%20Hammer%203%20hits%20combo%20in%20Unity/"/>
    <url>/codeArt-TechBlog/2024/06/28/Make%20Hammer%203%20hits%20combo%20in%20Unity/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Unity-Game-Play-View"><a href="#Unity-Game-Play-View" class="headerlink" title="Unity Game Play View"></a>Unity Game Play View</h2>  <video width="900" controls>  <source src="/themes/fluid/source/video/Hammer3Hit.mp4" type="video/mp4">  </video><h2 id="Design-and-Thoughts-Hammer-3-hits-combo"><a href="#Design-and-Thoughts-Hammer-3-hits-combo" class="headerlink" title="Design and Thoughts Hammer 3 hits combo"></a>Design and Thoughts Hammer 3 hits combo</h2><h3 id="key-pose-and-spacing"><a href="#key-pose-and-spacing" class="headerlink" title="key pose and spacing"></a>key pose and spacing</h3><ol><li>重量感 key pose and spacing</li><li>誇張 key pose</li><li>重量緩衝預備</li><li>重量與動作拉扯感</li></ol><h3 id="Some-Javascript"><a href="#Some-Javascript" class="headerlink" title="Some Javascript"></a>Some Javascript</h3><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">logSomething</span>(<span class="params">something</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Something&quot;</span>, something);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><h3 id="遊戲攻擊節奏-spacing"><a href="#遊戲攻擊節奏-spacing" class="headerlink" title="遊戲攻擊節奏 spacing"></a>遊戲攻擊節奏 spacing</h3><ol><li>強調重型武器的重量感，預備與緩衝動作間距小且速度慢，攻擊動作間距大且速度快，如下圖以 Attack 02 為例<ul><li>Attack02<img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/7b27393d-5a67-46b3-b5c0-7bdee16237ab/Untitled.png?id=00da788f-c743-4e61-b83b-465a62586f1f&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=oel0ne-0Vxp4spnVqh8DTv7B5EVh4vZXcst-c1BExAM&downloadName=Untitled.png" width="800" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"></li></ul></li><li>重型武器，hits ( atk01-40 frames、atk02-33 frames、atk03-56 frames ) 如下參考 3 hit combo<ul><li>當攻擊間距較大且速度快與預備緩衝間距小且速度慢，會形成反差的對比，玩家在體感上也較可以明顯感受武器的重量<video width="800" controls> <source src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/8edba7cf-7278-4405-bd39-0c59e5d1dee3/ANI_Player_Warhammer_3_hits_comb_comp.mp4?id=3992e3ae-5ff0-4968-b047-6b51a0220de3&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=TPRAJ4MX6-huHrz3j0e6IW9GshhedOhHWUr9wGjGhVw&downloadName=ANI_Player_Warhammer_3_hits_comb_comp.mp4" type="video/mp4"> </video></li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="Import-process-and-settings-build-game"><a href="#Import-process-and-settings-build-game" class="headerlink" title="Import process and settings &amp; build game"></a>Import process and settings &amp; build game</h2><details>  <summary>export animation & animation blended</summary><p>Assets：<br><img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/d1b1cf1c-c4c3-405a-b7a3-8f33193d85be/Untitled.png?id=75a25819-1db7-47fc-b456-056fae04ba0e&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=1IfGuFU3STFBs76SMeltK45eH7lqU5dFSp4hwnV8_Lg&downloadName=Untitled.png" width="400" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"></p><p>Setting up the animation and blending attributes：<br><img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/c4babe0e-9d85-4658-96df-baab5671ba67/Untitled.png?id=0aa20dd1-1801-417f-9d91-01f233348589&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=7LvxzHP2kNTR70k6YcBBCjCpCbO9xps-O0BJZY4vqYU&downloadName=Untitled.png" width="900" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"></p></details><details>  <summary>create prefab & export rig</summary>  assets：  <img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/a0a14d07-1fec-445e-a687-705401861e92/Untitled.png?id=450557f6-56dd-4a62-b9cf-e36697b2759b&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=4QmjH6egVvdX7vR3M5nWhEHrrFKRPCu-YUyrTNlQkoQ&downloadName=Untitled.png" width="900" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"><p>Setting up the character prefab and rig attributes：<br><img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/47f29b16-a6eb-424f-89b4-52aea9950dfc/Untitled.png?id=4ad43a5f-177c-4dd4-9783-dbd391c0c8eb&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=xZ9B6RLenm_pKjoHq2NBxmfLn5Q-L4xlnmyl_XKutt4&downloadName=Untitled.png" width="900" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"></p></details><details>  <summary>create player_camera</summary><h3 id="CameraFollow-cs"><a href="#CameraFollow-cs" class="headerlink" title="CameraFollow.cs"></a>CameraFollow.cs</h3><figure class="highlight cs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> UnityEngine;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">CameraFollow</span> : <span class="title">MonoBehaviour</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> Transform target; <span class="comment">// 角色的 Transform</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> Vector3 offset;   <span class="comment">// 相機和角色之間的偏移量</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">float</span> smoothSpeed = <span class="number">0.125f</span>; <span class="comment">// 平滑跟隨的速度</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">LateUpdate</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// 計算相機應該的位置</span></span><br><span class="line">      Vector3 desiredPosition = target.position + offset;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// 平滑移動相機到目標位置</span></span><br><span class="line">      Vector3 smoothedPosition = Vector3.Lerp(transform.position, desiredPosition, smoothSpeed);</span><br><span class="line">      transform.position = smoothedPosition;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// 確保相機朝向角色</span></span><br><span class="line">      transform.LookAt(target);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><details>  <summary>create scene & props</summary>  assets：  <img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/ea024785-8ad7-4c5e-9dfb-8b64c83bb13c/Untitled.png?id=af628c37-8984-447e-a6bc-ada209e7b243&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=ikjvCvxSk4r34EIUgP-xwI2YErIAZZH5j5iWq3eTdo8&downloadName=Untitled.png" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;">  processing：  <video width="900" controls>  <source src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/8473dce2-911e-4ebc-92ca-c4edf4db640d/My_project_-_SampleScene_-_Windows_Mac_Linux_-_Unity_2022.3.30f1___DX11__2024-05-27_13-42-56.mp4?id=d926803d-b3f3-403c-aaa5-3835b5e6d29b&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719475200000&signature=cYB_Ml7eR_kiBmGXUz_ESkcOMO3SYqWMdgvo7XJFCjs&downloadName=My+project+-+SampleScene+-+Windows%2C+Mac%2C+Linux+-+Unity+2022.3.30f1_+_DX11_+2024-05-27+13-42-56.mp4" type="video/mp4">  </video></details><details>  <summary>assign texture</summary></details><details>  <summary>add sounds to gameplay</summary>  <ol><li><p>assets：<br><img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/7a34d956-fc3f-4adc-bab4-1b391f69732b/Untitled.png?id=c4d5a628-d16d-44d7-b579-1994d4b94322&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719482400000&signature=rba3PS-iWXLBXF-ILjV3FZjyLh0dQ9K_F1PvBoyyioE&downloadName=Untitled.png" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"></p></li><li><p>setup in animation then add events to frmes bar：</p><img src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/a2b1317b-5ceb-407e-9354-5265d910ce25/Untitled.png?id=13f78cdc-8040-42f1-9db2-42d2f4d0e6a7&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719482400000&signature=6gju-06JVgyhNFqPuk33w_WBRcNFsQrLjLMfUq17afg&downloadName=Untitled.png" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"></li></ol></details><details>  <summary>setup animator controller</summary>  assets：  <img src="  https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/03fd7940-a3ab-482b-a7a6-2ce149f5c633/Untitled.png?id=28593c2b-01b8-478e-bf1c-7cdb1e9f198b&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719540000000&signature=-T7MedP0fViWuPmC8XaI8cVFXmElZbuCsobcLGkVimU&downloadName=Untitled.png" style="display: block; margin-left: 0;"><p>animator controller：<br><video width="900" controls></p>  <source src="https://file.notion.so/f/f/77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00/c9286f2b-4904-485a-b856-219404f94e97/My_project_-_SampleScene_-_Windows_Mac_Linux_-_Unity_2022.3.30f1__DX11__2024-05-27_00-15-14.mp4?id=a849697e-3e83-41e2-9c40-d968b8c323fd&table=block&spaceId=77941c6e-940b-4bec-9271-c1b44d34df00&expirationTimestamp=1719540000000&signature=jeQ6ciBaqCt5GYRqDNIUtXpJC1rIgPIlomZvb1-Vnl4&downloadName=My+project+-+SampleScene+-+Windows%2C+Mac%2C+Linux+-+Unity+2022.3.30f1+_DX11_+2024-05-27+00-15-14.mp4" type="video/mp4">  </video></details>]]></content>
    
    
